---
title: Smart Chipotle-Glazed Double Pork Chops with Warm Green Bean Potato Salad
description: BBQ chipotle-glazed pork chops get nicely charred under the broiler to give this dish sweet-smoky heat. It's paired with a warm potato salad with crunchy pickles and green beans.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/double-cotelettes-de-porc-glacees-au-chipotle-1efee8e4.jpg
